Create the art for a Magic The Gathering card called "Ace of Spades." Depict an elemental creature formed from swirling black smoke and shimmering metallic spade motifs, its body crackling with ethereal energy. The background is a mystical twilight, with faint playing card symbols shimmering in the air. Give the creature a powerful and elusive stance, with ghostly, semi-transparent edges, evoking a sense of mystery and magic.